-- Persian Gulf Equity Movers: Agility, Industries Qatar
-- B y   Z a h r a   H a n k i r
-- 2013-02-21T13:02:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-21/persian-gulf-equity-movers-agility-industries-qatar-correct-.html
Abu Dhabi’s ADX General Index rises
0.4% to 3,022.48, highest level since Oct. 2009, at close in
emirate, bringing gain this week to 3%; Dubai’s DFM General
Index little changed, Qatar QE Index -0.8%.  ADVANCERS:
* Agility (AGLTY KK) +1.8%; wins contract to manage Swedish
SSAB’s heavy plate export shipments, 2-yr contract has est.
value of $10m
* Du (DU UH) +0.2%, bringing rally this week to 15%; co. said
Feb. 19 net after royalty 994m dirhams vs 440m, proposes cash
DVD of 30 fils/shr  DECLINERS:
* Industries Qatar (IQCD QD) -0.5%; board to discuss financial
results
